Text: Re Revised EEI Collateral Annex Cc Here are PacifiCorps comments Although I still dont know that I understand the document I hope they are helpful Original Message From Andy Katz To Sent Friday September AM Subject Revised EEI Collateral Annex All Carol StClair has completed revisions to the Collateral Annex Attached please find clean and redlined versions and the annex coversheet Please provide Carol with any comments on this version and cc the rest of the working group so we know where everyone is coming from Thanks Andrew S Katz Director Industry Legal AffairsEdison Electric Institute Pennsylvania Avenue NWWashington DC Voice Fax email PPW comments to EEI Collateral Annex Revised adoc
